data.description: This home has storage galore with numerous built-in drawers and closets. The large eat in kitchen with lots of cabinets and a walk in pantry is perfect for mealtime. There is also a separate  dining room connected to the family room; perfect for entertaining. Don't miss the wood burning fireplace with a blower that keeps the great room toasty all winter long.  A gorgeous copper colored metal roof was installed in 2014 and has a lifetime warranty.  The large backyard has an abundantly producing apple tree, an oversized patio area, and a storage building and is surrounded by a cinderblock fence with metal gates. The landscaped front yard has a brick flowerbed with knockout roses and mature trees. This friendly established neighborhood boasts wide streets with ample parking and close to shopping and schools. The oversized 2 car garage includes a built in workbench. These are just some of the reasons to give this vintage beauty a look.
